<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><note xmlns="http://note.youdao.com" file-version="0" schema-version="1.0.3"><head/><body><para><coId>1118-1557967256713</coId><text>希沃教师空间可以让老师选择自己教学的课本，课本下有章节点，每个章节点下都有丰富的资源给老师进行备课。</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>1358-1557967423500</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>3118-1557967429452</coId><text>书本属性</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>3737-1557967479717</coId><text>学科，版本，学段，书名</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>6140-1557967492887</coId><text>语文，人教版，小学，六年级下册</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>6217-1557967429782</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><image><coId>5784-1557967533952</coId><source>http://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/9d8e7ec163346bfd38f130dff2631369/xmlnote/23996B7950B4486F91CA7BBF0BA29330/4982</source><text/><styles><width>580</width><height>1382</height></styles></image><para><coId>7979-1557967368584</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>9540-1557967543556</coId><text>上图为章节点结构，为树形结构，支持无限分级</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>1441-1557967548866</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>4532-1557967572506</coId><text>实现功能：</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>4377-1557967368734</coId><text>1.根据子章节，查询书本</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>4094-1557967291281</coId><text>2.根据书本查询所有章节</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>1690-1557967299450</coId><text>3.根据某个子章节查询章节路径 章=&gt;节=&gt;小节</text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>7140-1557967337414</coId><text>4.根据某个指定章节查询所有子节点 </text><inline-styles/><styles/></para><para><coId>3871-1557967550982</coId><text/><inline-styles/><styles/></para></body></note>